These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, orange, brown
House: craftsman, modern, farmhouse
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, frog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, volleyball, baseball
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who likes purple is between the modern house and the farmhouse house##2
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
5. the owner of the frog is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Color         | orange | purple   | brown   |
| House   | modern     | craftsman | farmhouse |
| Pet   | frog  | goldfish    | guinea-pig      |
| Sport     | volleyball     | water-polo      | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, september, april
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, handball
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, reading, traveling
House: farmhouse, futuristic, wooden
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the farmhouse house is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's birthday is in april##2
6. the person who's birthday is in april is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Birthday          | september  | october     | april     |
| Sport   | baseball     | handball     | cricket      |
| Hobby   | traveling  | reading | skydiving |
| House           | wooden | farmhouse     | futuristic       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, trike
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, juice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, techno, disco
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, american, argentine
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the fan disco##1
2. the canadian is between the person drinking juice and the fan disco##2
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
4. the american is the person driving the bus##1
5. the canadian is the fan techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Transport          | motorbike  | trike     | bus     |
| Beverage           | juice | lemonade  | tea   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | techno    | disco |
| Nationality           | argentine     | canadian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different games are played: chess, go, poker
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, hiking
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, van, motorbike
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person playing poker is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person driving the airplane##2
4. the person playing go is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Game    | chess       | poker  | go   |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks    | hiking  | gardening |
| Transport     | van   | motorbike | airplane        |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk     | water      |

