.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, mah-jongg
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, tram, train
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, november, february
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person drinking mirinda and the person driving the train##2
3. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Game          | mah-jongg    | monopoly     | backgammon      |
| Transport         | helicopter | tram | train |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | milk       | 7up       |
| Birthday           | november     | may       | february     |

