.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, water
There are 3 different nationalities: french, pakistani, american
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher, alhambra
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, basketball
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the american##1
2. the person drinking water is the french##1
3. the swisher-smoker is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's sport is rugby##2
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Beverage          | sprite | fanta | water    |
| Nationality         | pakistani | american      | french |
| Cigar   | old-henry   | swisher     | alhambra        |
| Sport           | rowing      | basketball       | rugby      |

