.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, pony
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lilac, grey
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, pall-mall, swisher
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, potato, apple
1. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating potato##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is between the person who likes lilac and the owner of the pony##2
5. the owner of the fish is the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Pet      | rabbit       | fish      | pony      |
| Color         | lilac    | grey | fuchsia      |
| Cigar           | swisher | davidoff     | pall-mall |
| Food   | potato     | apple          | pineapple       |

