.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
City: hamburg, colone, marseilles
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, dubstep, ambient
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, sports, romance
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching romance movies##2
2. the fan ambient is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
4. the fan dubstep is on the far left##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| City      | hamburg      | colone | marseilles     |
| Music-Genre          | dubstep   | trance      | ambient     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | mystery      | sports |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks | gardening        | singing     |

