.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, amaryllis, daisy
City: nizza, venice, new-york
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher, tiparillo
3 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, bridge
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
4. the person playing billiard is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to nizza##2
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Flower      | daisy     | amaryllis | lily      |
| City         | venice  | new-york       | nizza |
| Cigar   | tiparillo   | swisher         | old-henry     |
| Game   | monopoly | billiard    | bridge     |

