.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, bike, jet-ski
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, skiing, rugby
City: nizza, liverpool, venice
There 3 different types of food: garlic, kale, pumpkin
1. the person driving the bike is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person traveling to liverpool##2
6. the person traveling to nizza is the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Transport      | subway | bike      | jet-ski            |
| Sport           | tennis | rugby | skiing |
| City   | liverpool     | venice        | nizza         |
| Food   | kale  | garlic    | pumpkin        |

