3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the fan electronic##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan country##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| House      | tower    | colonial          | cottage |
| Sport          | cycling | badminton           | soccer        |
| Flower           | daffodil | azalea | orchid         |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | electronic    | country      |

