House: townhouse, modern, cottage
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, february
City: san-francisco, hannover, edinburgh
1. the modern house is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the townhouse house##2
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who growsrose##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the townhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Flower   | dahlia | rose  | orchid     |
| House   | cottage    | modern | townhouse |
| Birthday           | january        | february   | august  |
| City     | edinburgh      | hannover   | san-francisco |

