.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, november, july
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, azure, light-blue
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, dancer, journalist
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, sailing
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the journalist##1
2. the dancer is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the teacher is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who likes white##2
4. the dancer is the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's birthday is in november and the dancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Birthday      | january | july     | november        |
| Color         | azure   | light-blue | white |
| Job   | dancer        | teacher       | journalist      |
| Sport           | sailing           | lacrosse    | snowboarding       |

