.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, almond-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, montecristo, swisher
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, rosed-games, skydiving
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, iris, dahlia
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is rosed-games##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who's hobby is rosed-games is the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the swisher-smoker is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who's hobby is rosed-games##2
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage        | milk      | tea | almond-milk |
| Cigar         | montecristo     | swisher    | cain        |
| Hobby       | rosed-games | skydiving   | writing   |
| Flower   | rose          | iris     | dahlia       |

 